    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/01b9f6dcda8b6a4b61b4bc37ec4856f1.poster.avif?t=1764206226\" width=614 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/01b9f6dcda8b6a4b61b4bc37ec4856f1.webm?t=1764206226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/01b9f6dcda8b6a4b61b4bc37ec4856f1.mp4?t=1764206226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/8f143cb11057031c9a396f2555063a5a.webp?t=1764206226\" width=615 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Edwin Tevoran, infamous mercenary leader and erstwhile (self-proclaimed) war hero, has found himself in a predicament. The dubious schemes which once filled his coffers have all succumbed to ill fortune, leaving him in penniless desperation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/8f68cc0dc61c657b81c7c1b193b882e0.avif?t=1764206226\" width=615 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, when a serendipitous discovery spawns new designs for the petty criminality Tevoran loves so dearly, the door is opened to a chain of events that will forever change the course of the city of Tierva and beyond!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/26577f4913a96280145eff47737afa70.poster.avif?t=1764206226\" width=614 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/26577f4913a96280145eff47737afa70.webm?t=1764206226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/26577f4913a96280145eff47737afa70.mp4?t=1764206226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/212a37ec472905fc94fd7d96e4a6f8c5.webp?t=1764206226\" width=615 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn skills to unlock special attacks and abilities. Find, plunder, buy and sell items and equipment. Use terrain, traps, obstacles and even foes’ corpses to your tactical advantage as you lead Tevoran &amp; Company to questionable victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/7e1692369aa91411659daa9166dbf766.avif?t=1764206226\" width=614 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
